cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper deals with deep learning for state estimation problems such as tracking, navigation, and pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses uncertainty modeling and quantification, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
